June 5, 2006

 

 

 

TO:                  Coaches, Parents, and Athletes

FROM:            Joanne Slaton-Camargo

SUBJECT:       PAC Championships

                        Team Performance Lists

 

Our first championship meet is this weekend at Pinole High School.  This is our first time using the Club Manager Program so wanted to try something different.  I have therefore decided to post the team entry performance lists for your inspection.  Please check to make sure all your entries are correct.  If corrections are necessary, immediately email Anthony with your corrections by Wednesday, June 7th.  We will officially close everything at that time.  These are all entries received as of today, June 5, 2006.  ajcam@sbcglobal.net    

 

For the majority of teams and individuals who used the program and kept the doors of communication open, things went pretty well.  For those of you who have yet to use the program, please do so; it’s a requirement for the JO Championships June 23-25 at Granada High School in Livermore.

 

See team performance lists below:
